OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy during the evening with further
OL,7,Fshowers. More in the way of clear
OL,8,Fspells overnight before cloud and
OL,9,Fshowery rain return towards morning.
OL,10,FBecoming windy over the north coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA cloudy start with showery
OL,13,Frain then becoming drier and brighter
OL,14,Flater in the morning. A mainly dry
OL,15,Fafternoon with sunny intervals, the
OL,16,Fodd shower over Moray and north
OL,17,FAberdeenshire.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
