OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,6,Ftouch of frost early Wednesday then
OL,7,Fmainly dry and bright. Rain or showers
OL,8,Fon Thursday and Friday. Rather cold at
OL,9,Ffirst but temperatures recovering from
OL,10,FThursday.
